    "Table 4 presents the memory usage rates of the PoW, PoS, and PoA mechanisms.",
    "According to these results, the PoS mechanism gives the highest results for both sensitive and nonsensitive data.",
    "The PoS mechanism is followed by the PoA mechanism.",
    "The PoW mechanism gives the best result in terms of memory usage.",
    "As seen in the last row of Table 4, PoW provides approximately 23% better results than PoA and approximately 32% better results than PoS for sensitive data."
